        <div class="ArticleImgContent">
            <h2><a href="/en/dep/hod/Subjects/the-department-of-public-health/national-strategy-for-prevention-of-infe.html?id=528882">National strategy for prevention of infections in the health service and antibiotic resistance (2008–2012) in Norway</a></h2>        
                
            <p>
               The strategy includes relevant measures in many sectors and at various levels that should enable us to continue to maintain a favourable situation with regards to hospital infections and antibiotic use in Norway. 
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
    


<div class="ArticleView">
        <img src="/upload/BLD/Ingresssbilder/KLL_100x75jpg.jpg" alt="" class="ArticleImg" />
        
        
        <div class="ArticleImgContent">
            <h2><a href="/en/dep/hod/Subjects/the-department-of-public-health/action-plan-for-combating-female-genital.html?id=524234">Action Plan for Combating Female Genital Mutilation 2008-2011</a></h2>        
                
            <p>
               This Action Plan is the result of the joint efforts of seven ministries. The responsibility for coordinating
the work to combat female genital mutilation lies with the Ministry of Children and Equality.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    
    


