            <p>
               Report No. 20 to the Storting (2006-2007) National strategy to reduce social inequalities in health
Recommendation from the Ministry of Health and Care Services, dated 9 February 2007, approved in the Council of State on the same date (The Second Stoltenberg Government).


            </p>
            
        </div>
